# 🧩 CForum – Terminal-Based Multi-User Forum

**Author:** Sakshi Narvekar  
**B-number:** [Your B-number here]  
**Course:** [Course Name / ID]

---

## ✅ Overview

CForum is a terminal-based forum system that allows multiple users to:
- View existing topics
- Create new discussion threads
- Reply to topics with messages

All data is **persisted** in `forum.txt` and restored on each run.

---

## 🛠️ How to Build & Run

```bash
make        # Compiles the app
./cforum    # Starts the forum system
